-----------------------------INSTALL HADOOP-------------------------------
1. link install hadoop : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GNnt6L3AsDU
2. link configuration  : https://hadoop.apache.org/docs/r3.2.1/hadoop-project-dist/hadoop-common/SingleCluster.html


-------------------------------START HADOOP-------------------------------
1. start hadoop     : 1. sbin/start-yarn.sh
	              2. sbin/start-dfs.sh
2. open hadoop 	    : localhost	:8088
3. open namenode    : localhost	:


------------------------------keluar dari environmen anak conda-------------------------
1. conda deactivate


